{
  "stem": "3952.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They said, ladies separately and-- and men separately.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in the first time with my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And an officer with a dog, with a huge dog.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And later we find out that his name was Mengele.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked my father, how old are you?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, 56.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He moved-- he made like this, a movement to one side.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he asked me how old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, 17.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He made a movement this side.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's when I saw my father last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's when I saw my family last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My-- after we jumped out of the wagons, I didn't even see the girls.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't even see my mother, because they were a little bit further, another line, and they were not in the first line.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I couldn't see them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, because the coming-- we were-- we were always hoping we would hear some good news.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Getting out of the train was so in a rush, so fast, so with-- with the noise, [SPEAKING GERMAN], this yelling and barking of the dogs, that you couldn't think of saying goodbye to anybody.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never said goodbye to my father who was right near me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We never-- didn't-- we were just waiting, what will happen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then suddenly, I found myself alone, and I wanted to go to the-- they told us that these are electric wires.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted to go to the electric wires.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, you wouldn't even reach the wire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would shoot you before you reach the wire, because they-- they had-- they had these towers with the SS people with rifles.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I wanted to go to the wires.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What am I-- what, am I gonna be alone?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No mother, no father, nobody from the family?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
